<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(فَإِنَّهُ)</span> أَيِ الصَّوْمَ <span class="c2">(لَهُ)</span> أَيْ لِلْفَرْجِ <span class="c2">(وِجَاءٌ)</span> بِكَسْرِ الْوَاوِ وَالْمَدِّ أَيْ كَسْرٌ شَدِيدٌ يَذْهَبُ بِشَهْوَتِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>